channel.description:
This is my first attempt on a practical script. It is now complete, please post your progress reports  :) ;)

[u][b]Features:[/b][/u]
Rotates map if tree cannot be found.
Randomly rotated map.
Effective ent detection.
Detects first free inv slot (see below).
Fast tree detection.
Decent anti-randoms (detects talking randoms quickly =P)
 --[i]Logs out if unsolvable random is found[/i]
Complete report
Good anti-randoms

[u][b]Lacking (Coming soon):[/b][/u]
Detect all axes broken/lost
Multiplayer

[u][b]Instructions:[/b][/u]
Put all items in the first inventory slots. If you skip [u]any[/u] slots, some logs will be skipped and/or other items will be dropped. I recommend getting 5 steel axes, wielding one and putting 4 on the top 4 inventory slots. It detects the last used slot, and drops everything after that. Don't start with logs in your inventory, they [u]will[/u] be skipped. Always have at least one axe in your inventory. If you have one axe, dont wield it (this doesn't apply yet, but it will when I make axe detection).

Start Runescape with Low Detail, Unsigned client. Set your computer to 32-bit colors. Scar 3.12c and SRL 4 required.

